N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 333.2 - Failure to distribute ballot

State Regulations

In the event that the board of elections of any county
shall not mail or otherwise distribute ballots to the military voters of such
county, board of elections shall notify the division in writing of the facts
and reasons for noncompliance with the provision of section 306 of the Election

Law. Notes
